{"tid":786192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"破紀錄！早9日嚟排隊瞓街 為搶$1電競筆電","createTime":"2018-08-19T17:47:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:26:50.000Z","uid":71543,"like":95,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"b9c29789677fffc5639fe3e2d6e5f4979421f72c","tid":786192,"uid":71543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:47:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdLivCt4viY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrdLivCt4viY&d=Kgbc78tU3mnYTkYgND5%2Fltr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=b3ada33a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rdLivCt4viY</a><br />\n「2018腦場電腦節」會在8月22至28日，假深水埗腦場舉行，想不到者在8月13日，腦場一放出排隊龍頭位置，已經有人在該日的下午到來排隊。<br />\n<br />\n就肥通現在收到的消息，暫時腦場電腦節的$1優惠產品名單還未落實，但排隊人士不約而同表示，會鎖定購買電競筆電，排頭位的劉生表示：「以腦場電腦節的慣例，都會有$1電競筆電或桌面電腦，雖然$1優惠物品名單未出，但我都相信一定會有的。」<br />\n<br />\n排第二位的13歲李小朋友表示，他所鎖定購買的$1產品也是電競筆電：「如果到時電競筆電只有一部，或許我會買電競桌上電腦吧！」<br />\n今次排隊的頭兩位，分別在在9日前的中午，及8日前的早上來排隊，比較往年的最早排隊人龍紀錄，都只是7日前，可說是打破了多年來的紀錄。"},{"pid":"d6a17c48e17580e0d772f94699d38a41263dc3de","tid":786192,"uid":43575,"like":372,"dislike":20,"score":352,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:50:19.000Z","msg":"番十日工都有幾千蚊買到電腦啦<br />\n排隊十日唔沖涼污糟辣撻"},{"pid":"0ce036fda05e2cd672ee1072ae10c82c26d8345a","tid":786192,"uid":71543,"like":341,"dislike":5,"score":336,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:50:23.000Z","msg":"13歲細路係ssp排通宵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過幾晚南亞狗連後門都玩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a92c68fbef5fbe70ed992d4c7fb1e47af25b734","tid":786192,"uid":4780,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:52:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdb8dbed92676359e4edd7f946582853011c2973","tid":786192,"uid":77196,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:22:58.000Z","msg":"行雷閃電<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\